dcterms:description: This dataset contains audio and video recordings of a wooden drumstick probing indoor and outdoor environments by hitting, scraping, and poking different objects of different material densities. It explores the rich timbres arising out of the interactions between the wooden drumstick and various hard and soft surfaces such as tree trunks, dirt, leaves, metal cans, ceramic mugs, carpets, soft cushions, etc.
dcterms:title: The Greatest Hits Dataset
